{"tid":2213874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文匯大公 星島 明報 成香港官方認可傳媒","createTime":"2020-09-23T00:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T03:09:27.000Z","uid":13745,"like":10,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3c2a482b700ca78cef7fe122f14ed7de2ed0c301","tid":2213874,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:55:39.000Z","msg":"教育局破天荒只安排《大公報》、《文匯報》、《星島日報》和《明報》作小圈子採訪，由主席陳黃麗娟「導讀」。有議員炮轟教局審查傳媒。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，有電子傳媒曾向教育局查詢可否參與上述小圈子採訪，對方回應只有「少量被揀選的報紙」才能參與，又聲稱只是主席陳黃麗娟向記者「導讀」報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200923/DJXIUJYSVBD5TFXWJEUJ7S2C7I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200923%2FDJXIUJYSVBD5TFXWJEUJ7S2C7I%2F&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2zDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=b84152bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200923%2FDJXIUJYSVBD5TFXWJEUJ7S2C7I%2F&h=fcca00a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200923/DJXIUJYSVBD5TFXWJEUJ7S2C7I/</a>"},{"pid":"42b7b9a381e3dbcba9797acdd90b8359c08e0f57","tid":2213874,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:56:35.000Z","msg":"中宣部媒體認證 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcfd83b28d1426be71a7c1674e0d497d6ff224dd","tid":2213874,"uid":254594,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:56:50.000Z","msg":"百份都唔撚比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ca03f3e9e7c0f3a56813b00f785c4aadafa5eb","tid":2213874,"uid":18477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bcfd83b28d1426be71a7c1674e0d497d6ff224dd","tid":2213874,"uid":254594,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:56:50.000Z","msg":"百份都唔撚比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:59:14.000Z","msg":"如果過幾日將呢四間作文公司放入sanction list會點呢<img src=\"/assets/fa